Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:04.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, it's Chinatown in Yokohama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The surprising people Ran got involved with!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who presented the "Opinion on Twelve Matters" to Emperor Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyoyuki Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the term for a Pureland Buddhist painting that depicts the descent of Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoju Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Can you knock it off?\NThat stuff gives me hives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a big Japanese history test tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I've been too busy with karate to study for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should've stayed home tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who won us that free meal at Chinatown Restaurant, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're telling me to stay home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! Just shut the book until we get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I won't have time to study tonight!\NThere's a ton of great stuff on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading in the car is gonna make you carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I've got a tough semicircular canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}For some reason, it brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man in the cap, standing in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I can't remember {\i1}where{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A back street in an unfamiliar city...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:36.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Every time I try, I just see that image of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Standing in the rain, just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:47.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the look on Shin'ichi's face, kind but sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you drenched in rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tell me, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your forehead went all wrinkly and your face got scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't remember the answer to this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the Cloistered Rule Period,\NKiyohira Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nuts. Guess I {\i1}have{\i0} gotten carsick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as we're about to start filming,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,our lead actress breaks a bone in a motorcycle accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:53.93,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaizo Isogami (52)\NMovie Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just stop trying to make this movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, we can't pass up an opportunity like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the sequel to a blockbuster, and it's already attracting buzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:10.53,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Motohiro Ito (38)\NAssistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With our actress injured, we're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the only girl we've found who can play this role!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we keep trying to film this picture, the body count...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will only go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:18.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Keigo Kitaura (29)\NOriginal Author
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm glad that actress pulled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never fit my image of the heroine of my novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitaura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:39.56,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiro Kawabata (46)\NProducer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn... Why can't we find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cute young girl, who can handle action scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, we can't use this gift certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the restaurant's name is written right on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's us... We issued the coupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why can't we use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I demand an explanation and a clear one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kiddo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your sister's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who...am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of joint is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you pick your customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You snobs think you can mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take this outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to strong-arm us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not going anywhere until we get an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The certificate says clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not valid on Sundays or holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's right! It's here in the small print!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I sincerely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. We're happy that you understand the provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, why didn't you check in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what? You're the one who rushed out first, saying that early bird catches the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, young lady, that was a good kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you and me going to see a Bruce Lee movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.77,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mike Hama\NPrivate Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mike Hama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mike Hama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard that name before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This guy is Mike Hama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got an office on the second floor of Yokohama Nichigeki in Kogane-cho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:08:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That second-rate private eye who has an office on the second floor of a movie theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, lady, call me when you feel like going out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dinner, sir... What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll pick up the check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A heroine in a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're perfect for the role!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're interested in the part...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll just forget your lines and make a laughingstock of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not everyone is blessed with my oratory skills, my power to entrance a crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your power to {\i1}sleep{\i0}, while I put on a show for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the movie's a hit, you'll be a star! You'll be in showbiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll hobnob with movie stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention baseball players, soccer stars, Formula 1 drivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll travel the world for the film. America, England, France...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Go for it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Take on challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to do it,\Nyou'd better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Some filmmakers will completely ignore the original story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to add a racy love scene or similar junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Love scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitaura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}! You're not talking about {\i1}me{\i0}, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On second thought, say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's all wrong for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if doing one little love scene scares you, don't sign on for this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show business can be the death of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop scaring her! This girl here is our golden goose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... I'm nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'll just wipe it up with my hot towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Can I get a new pair of chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a fever. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! It's just a little head cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if you collapse like last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't listen to your hard-headed dad! Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you want and I'll bring it to you on a platter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I thought I said not to order the century eggs or the crab omelette!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm allergic to eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even stand to {\i1}look{\i0} at egg dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, young lady, eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want curry with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, this is a Chinese restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't have curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want curry! Curry, curry, curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they don't have curry, I don't wanna eat here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we should go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Have some Chinese dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really liked these the last time we had them, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez. Doesn't she care about my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh well. Where's the soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, in front of the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn. It's in front of the old guy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, the soy sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay, the chili oil is in front of that fox-faced guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! You want the chili oil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She has to do everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Peking duck here is superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have any favorite actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is Yukiko Fujimine{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the mother of one of my best friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I've looked up to her since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other is an American actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sharon Vineyard{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she passed away a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! A great actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I met her once and she was really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey where'd you meet a star like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nowhere you'd know, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko Fujimine and Sharon Vineyard? You've got taste, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're both legendary performers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:14:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't died, she might've become a legend like those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Shiro Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 46, a movie producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death seems to be asphyxiation caused by potassium cyanide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly. Potassium cyanide, arsenic, caustic soda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do criminals keep getting their hands on this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did this guy put anything into his mouth before he dropped dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The waiter wrapped the duck in crêpes and placed them on the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim went into convulsions the moment he bit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So his last supper was Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least he went out on a high note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no poison was found in the Peking duck,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the waiter didn't have any cyanide on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the victim must've had the poison on his hands before he picked up the duck crêpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the person who poisoned this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is one of you guys who were eating with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you guys know the stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in the movie biz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The star of our latest project got in an accident before we started shooting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we were discussing what to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we find a replacement, or ditch the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this girl and her family walked in, and Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw something in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He invited them to come have dinner with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You with the mustache! I've seen you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you have! I'm..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an ex-con, right?\NOr a wanted man on the run?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri? You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As in the famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that cheap con man called "Smoking Kogoro", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}Sleeping{\i0} Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We've got a cyanide reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find any traces of poison in the other dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we've found evidence of potassium cyanide
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the chopsticks, plate and hot towel the victim was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was sitting next to the victim when he collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sitting on his right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on his left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sitting to his left, eating dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this case is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer poisoned his own towel and switched it with the victim's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't suspect a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were on his right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the victim was right-handed, he would've placed his towel right next to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew he'd wipe his hands on the towel before picking up the duck crêpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I seen {\i1}you{\i0} somewhere too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he looks familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've never met! I just know your face from TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were forced to shave your head because you screwed up a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to be embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I like the new look better than that doofy old perm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking about my twin brother Sango! He works for the Shizuoka Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.70,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jugo Yokomizo\NKanazawa Prefectural Police\NInspector
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Jugo Yokomizo, an inspector for the Kanagawa Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother is easy-going and seems to respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't trust private eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you make of this mark on the victim's jeans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like some kind of stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spilled it on him when I was sitting next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You were next to the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you and the kid were sitting next to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} switched seats. He forced himself between me and Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, Conan sat next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So before he moved, he was sitting between the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I ended up next to him after Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} invited the detective to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the detective and his family joined us, Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was sitting between him and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but our chairs were pretty far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was on the other side of the table the whole time. I'm innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know {\i1}after{\i0} the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you check his trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} changed seats after the soup was spilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he used his towel to wipe it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you check the stain, you can see whether the towel was poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Uncle Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's no trace of poison on his trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you checked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the waiter told us he gave the victim a fresh pair of chopsticks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after his first ones fell on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we didn't find any cyanide on the chopsticks either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the towel was poisoned {\i1}after{\i0} the soup was spilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the waiter brought the new chopsticks and the victim switched seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're still the chief suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I poison a guy I'd just met at a restaurant I'd never been to before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your story sounds too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The minute you show up at this place, your daughter gets scouted for a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a total coincidence that we came here the same time as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, I met that man on a rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:22.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe he just looks like somebody I know, like that inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:25.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All I can dredge up are three faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:32.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A smiling mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Angry eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:36.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't hear you, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay! Just felt a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a seat! I'm sure Uncle will crack the case soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't get in the way, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:20.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:24.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:27.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We have to get her to a hospital soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the towel into the restroom and poisoned it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can't even stand to look at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anything else on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.61,0:24:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, I see... Nothing else on it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.43,0:24:30.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot towel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.96,0:24:38.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Mike Hama, Private Eye", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The old guy's got the same nonchalance, at least.
